      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3173_0009"/>de <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">berlin</rs>
                  25111 17 <date>6</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>9-35,–m</time>=</dateline></opener><p><rs type="work" ref="#pmb41531">tageblatt</rs> bringt <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02657-1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb88513" subtype="implied">ankuendigung</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02657-1">»<quote><rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb88513">Im <rs type="org" ref="#pmb35597"><hi rend="spaced-out">Deutschen Theater</hi></rs> soll ›<rs ref="#pmb29857" type="work"><hi rend="spaced-out">Der Schleier der Beatrice</hi></rs>‹</rs> von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121"><hi rend="spaced-out">Arthur Schnitzler</hi></rs> noch in diesem Monat zur Aufführung kommen. Die Hauptrollen spielen <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12977">Irene Triesch</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10844">Bassermann</rs>. Im <hi rend="spaced-out">Mai</hi> gastiert
                     das <rs type="org" ref="#pmb35597">Deutsche Theater</rs> im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50"><hi rend="spaced-out">Wien</hi></rs><hi rend="spaced-out">er</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="org" ref="#pmb63031">Karl-Theater</rs>.</quote>« <bibl>In: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb41531">Berliner Tageblatt</rs>, Jg. 32, Nr. 65,
                        <date>5. 2. 1904</date>, Abendblatt, S. 3</bibl>.</note> dass <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29857">beatrice</rs> noch diesen monat aufgefuehrt wird.</p><closer>gruss = <signed>goldmann .+</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
